AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label :NFDI_0001211 "linked data portal"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> :NFDI_0001211 "A Linked Data Portal is a data portal that supports the publication, access, and exploration of linked datasets using semantic web technologies and standardized data formats.")
